__________('keyboard',)__________


Positive Reviews:

---'I have used this phone for over a year now and here are some pros and consCons:-I had to replace the handset once after six months with keyboard and other hard key problems.- lack of useful apps- have to reboot after you install and uninstall apps to use them-ridiculously slow in downloading and installing apps- Got very sluggish over time and freezes often- only way to reboot is by taking the battery out.- Touch screen is not very responsive.' **** 'other'

Negative Reviews:

---'This is not the only phone with a sliding keyboard but this is probably the best engineered one.' **** 'best'


